channel.title: [Release]Katana[Release]
channel.description:
Well, i decided to release my "Oriental Katana" from awhile back. it is triangulated and modified to be client capable. i did not, however, make it into .DAT or anything as well, i dont have datmaker, and i dont have a server so why waste my time to do so after ive already wasted time taking it from 90,000 faces to 2,300 triangulated ones? non the less, here it is:
Screenshot: [IMG]http://i369.photobucket.com/albums/oo131/0xXDylanXx0/sword.jpg[/img]
Download Link: [url=http://]http://www.mediafire.com/?deg32byijnj[/url]

Look, here’s the original: http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,362881.0.html[/quote]
